title: Astros take 2-1 series lead over Royals with 4-2 win
text:
> Top News Astros take 2-1 series lead over Royals with 4-2 win Houston Astros' Colby Rasmus, right, watches his pop up hit the roof as Kansas City Royals catcher Salvador Perez, left, looks on during the eighth inning in Game 3 of baseball's American League Division Series Sunday, Oct. 11, 2015, in Houston. Rasmus was safe at first on the play. (AP Photo/Pat Sullivan) The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
